<style>
.fn-v2-section {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #fff;
}

.fn-v2-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
}

.fn-v2-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    padding: 64px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: stretch;
}

/* Copy */
.fn-v2-copy {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    justify-content: center;
}

.fn-v2-heading {
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 500 !important;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #141414;
    letter-spacing: 0 !important;
    margin: 0;
}

.fn-v2-text {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #141414;
    margin: 0;
}

.fn-v2-text p {
    margin: 0 0 1em;
}

.fn-v2-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.fn-v2-text strong {
    font-weight: 700;
}

/* Signature */
.fn-v2-signature {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 8px;
}

.fn-v2-signature img {
    max-width: 176px;
    height: 60px;
    object-fit: contain;
}

.fn-v2-sig-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: normal;
    color: #672666;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.84px;
}

.fn-v2-sig-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: normal;
    color: #141414;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.72px;
    margin-left: 12px;
}

/* Image */
.fn-v2-image {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.fn-v2-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 16px;
}

/* ===== Responsive ===== */
@media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .fn-v2-container { padding: 40px 32px; }
    .fn-v2-card { padding: 40px; gap: 40px; }
    .fn-v2-heading { font-size: 26px; }
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
    .fn-v2-container { padding: 40px 16px; }
    .fn-v2-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        gap: 24px;
    }
    .fn-v2-heading { font-size: 24px; }
    .fn-v2-image {
        order: -1;
    }
}
</style>

<div class="fn-v2-container">
    <div class="fn-v2-card">
        <div class="fn-v2-copy">
            <h2 class="fn-v2-heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
            <div class="fn-v2-text">{{ section.settings.text }}</div>
            <div class="fn-v2-signature">
                {% if section.settings.signature_image != blank %}
                    <img src="{{ section.settings.signature_image | image_url: width: 400 }}" alt="{{ section.settings.signature_name }}" loading="lazy">
                {% endif %}
                <div>
                    <span class="fn-v2-sig-name">– {{ section.settings.signature_name }}</span><br>
                    <span class="fn-v2-sig-title">{{ section.settings.signature_title }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% if section.settings.image != blank %}
            <div class="fn-v2-image">
                <img src="{{ section.settings.image | image_url: width: 1000 }}" alt="{{ section.settings.heading }}" loading="lazy">
            </div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
    "name": "Founder Note V2",
    "class": "fn-v2-section",
    "settings": [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "id": "heading",
            "label": "Heading",
            "default": "A Note from Our Founder"
        },
        {
            "type": "richtext",
            "id": "text",
            "label": "Text",
            "default": "<p>Look, I know you're skeptical. <strong>You should be.</strong> You've spent years and hundreds of dollars on products that promised to fix your sleep and didn't.</p><p>I'm not going to tell you Rejuvia is magic. It's not. It's mint-flavored spray made from 13 plants and herbs that your great-grandmother probably could have named.</p><p><strong>The only thing we did differently is put them in a format your body can actually absorb. That's it. That's the whole innovation.</strong></p><p>If it doesn't work for you, email us within 90 days and <strong>we'll refund every cent.</strong> Try one bottle. Give it a few nights. And if you don't notice a difference, it costs you nothing.</p><p><strong>That's a fair deal from a family that just wants you to sleep.</strong></p>"
        },
        {
            "type": "image_picker",
            "id": "image",
            "label": "Photo"
        },
        {
            "type": "image_picker",
            "id": "signature_image",
            "label": "Signature image"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "id": "signature_name",
            "label": "Name",
            "default": "RC Williams"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "id": "signature_title",
            "label": "Title",
            "default": "Founder"
        }
    ],
    "presets": [
        {
            "name": "Founder Note V2",
            "category": "Custom"
        }
    ]
}
{% endschema %}
